      <title>社交媒体巨头回避学区对成瘾问题的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/social-media-giants-avoid-school-districts-addiction-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 和其他社交媒体公司在数百起由学区提起的诉讼中驳回了新的索赔，这些诉讼旨在收回解决学生使用社交媒体所造成的负面影响的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/social-media-giants-avoid-school-districts-addiction-claims</guid>
